                {
                    "id" : "prerequisites",
                    "text" : [ { "text" : "### Pre-requisites\n\nIn the first two chapters of this section, we studied counting, number organization, and the initial concept of limits. Afterward, we explored the principle of comparisons. In this chapter, we begin studying how to navigate the number system. Therefore, we recommend studying the previous two chapters before proceeding with this one",
                                 "source" : [ 
                                              { "type": 1,
                                                "uuid": "b5efc8f9-c268-430f-9681-7a43848ee48e",
                                                "text": "History Tracers Team",
